JAKARTA, June 1 (Xinhua)--Indonesian Attorney General Soedjono C. Atmonegoro said here Monday that an investigation on the wealth of former government officials, including former President Soeharto and his family, was going on.
 JAKARTA, June 9 (Xinhua)--The office of Indonesia's attorney general has formed a team to investigate the wealth of present and former Indonesian government officials, a spokesman of the office said here Tuesday.
 Soedjono said that he has assigned junior Attorney General to carry out the investigation.